snippet.title: Slay the Princess - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description: It's almost time for the world to end. Check out the latest trailer for Slay the Princess and prepare for your mission in this horror RPG/visual novel game. Slay the Princess will be available on PC on October 20, 2023.
